Package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.archive

Class MotorEncoderController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.archive.MotorEncoderController
  • public class MotorEncoderController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class controls the motors and encoders, initializing their directions and providing common functions such as simple movements and actions.
